{"tid":886702,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"Pokémon帶旺台南吸金7,600萬","createTime":"2018-11-02T09:49:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-02T11:37:39.000Z","uid":25558,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"82cfabc14351041761488a9b89ce28381f001a64","tid":886702,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T09:49:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20181102/20536456\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181102%2F20536456&d=%2FwvC0QD7q%2Bc%2B2coBXKGRyUbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=77c07a08\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181102%2F20536456&h=17a15487\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20181102/20536456</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年11月02日 <br />\n<br />\nPok&eacute;mon帶旺台南吸金7,600萬<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20181102/large/a2102a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20181102%2Flarge%2Fa2102a.gif&h=e4c4e240&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n台南奇美博物館湧入大批捉精靈玩家。台灣《蘋果日報》<br />\n<br />\n「Pok&eacute;mon GO Safari Zone in Tainan」昨起在台南連刮5天捉精靈旋風，台南市府觀旅局透露，這次用遊戲觀光作行銷，為當地旅業帶來人潮與錢潮，5天捉寶活動保守預估會吸引20萬人次進入台南，為觀光、餐飲、伴手禮、交通等產業帶來3億元新台幣（下同，約7,632萬港元的）。<br />\n<br />\n台南市政府費時兩年爭取和遊戲公司合作，結合30個觀光區讓民眾和遊客捉精靈，為當地旅遊業打開一線生機。台南市觀光局長王時思昨表示，經過遊戲公司與在地電訊業者比對玩家登入賬號及停留時間後，首日捉精靈人數在奇美博物館主會場超過6.5萬人，全台南市也逾10萬人，數字已扣除飛人與一人擁有多支手機情況，當局原先預估5天應可吸20萬人潮，目前有信心突破30萬人。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20181102/large/a2102b.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20181102%2Flarge%2Fa2102b.gif&h=6a4be5a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n家長為孩子穿上比卡超服裝。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「比陸客來台還有用」<br />\n<br />\n這次行銷活動，市府花在交通與硬體設施、餐費、行政活動等開銷約共360萬元（約92萬港元），最終換來逾3億元的收入，台南業者開心地說，「寶可夢比陸客來台還有用」。<br />\n<br />\n台灣《蘋果日報》  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n湖南販賣器官猖獗殮房屍遭挖雙眼　家屬崩潰警拘4人<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n深圳歡樂谷架空觀光列車相撞"},{"pid":"be996e06285224dd305df03bee74e93ed7f3772a","tid":886702,"uid":23369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T10:03:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n<br />\n台灣《蘋果日報》  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n湖南販賣器官猖獗殮房屍遭挖雙眼　家屬崩潰警拘4人<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n深圳歡樂谷架空觀光列車相撞</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e5c319730c4996531f4b0e2f0d26edb4ef7b2a0","tid":886702,"uid":28743,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T10:04:36.000Z","msg":"最後個段<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c89291c2149ac06b0b2c9c33b7f2a09fe0e13ad9","tid":886702,"uid":165361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T11:21:09.000Z","msg":"真吸金<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4c3cf53c3d07eec74dd1a2df5c1476b751c7a3d","tid":886702,"uid":165361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T11:23:21.000Z","msg":"人地政府真係出錢出力同佢地傾"},{"pid":"69077b6cfd639e62a103adc22643238b3e265ae1","tid":886702,"uid":35746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T11:25:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85d37c69e810520836abaa88f0566a5c6b7712c1","tid":886702,"uid":75156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T11:37:39.000Z","msg":"香港政府<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ： Game?撚有錢搵咩 咪阻撚住我金融條水"}]}